title: Microsoft Azure Storage Accounts: Data Flow
agents: azure
catalog: cloud/azure
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check reports metrics regarding data flow of monitored
 azure storage accounts.
 You can configure levels for ingress, egress and transaction
 count.
 In order to use this check, you need to onfigure the Azure special agent.

item:
 The name of the resource.

discovery:
 One service is created for each storage account if all required metrics
 (total_Ingress, total_Egress, total_Transactions) are given.
